MASCARA • Nars Climax Mascara

🌺Okay, where do I begin.. This trip was so special, first of all, we fell in love with Bora Bora. Never did I think I would ever go there but always dreamt of going. We got to bond and spend time with friends and make amazing relationships with new friends. Normally I spend a lot of time alone editing, writing and being creative so being surrounded by other people in this industry who go through the exact same experiences and day to day lives really makes me happy as my personality yearns for friendships and being able to love my friends. I just feel overwhelmed with happiness and gratefulness. I’m so appreciative for all my experiences I get to live as I only lived this life in my dreams and can’t believe this is real.
I really came from nothing at all. All I had were my dreams and nothing to lose so I took many leaps of faith and did what I loved with the little that I had. If I was able to come this far, then you can too. All you need is a dream and a drive to go far. Thank you @narsissist for making my dreams come true and for the most beautiful trip. #NARSissist
